{"tid":1235151,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"【有後門?!】華為完美示範植入式廣告新招!!手機鎖屏強制出現廣告","createTime":"2019-06-17T05:22:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T06:31:32.000Z","uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"db165d703b1eb943dbff770df6f9a0369dea74d1","tid":1235151,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:22:00.000Z","msg":"在美國政府實施禁令後，華為處於危機之中，頒報的禁令禁止華為從美國公司包括 Qualcomm、Intel、GlobalFoundries、Arm、Teradyne 等採購其供應鏈組件，就連合作夥伴之一的 Google 亦有可能停止為華為提供部份手機軟件業務及支援，讓華為陷入困境。在如此嚴峻的時間，華為又爆出另一件「醜聞」，有用戶投訴在華為手機鎖屏後竟然出現了上旅遊網站 <a href=\"http://Booking.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FBooking.com&d=goC%2B%2BwCxwRgX8SEPTes0u4eNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=a83ec650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Booking.com</a> 的廣告，唔通就係「植入式廣告新招」?!<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n據報導，有不少使用華為手機的用戶發現，手機在鎖定螢幕時竟然無故出現了旅遊網站 <a href=\"http://Booking.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FBooking.com&d=goC%2B%2BwCxwRgX8SEPTes0u4eNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=a83ec650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Booking.com</a> 的廣告，用戶若果使用預設的風景桌布，就會出現 <a href=\"http://Booking.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FBooking.com&d=goC%2B%2BwCxwRgX8SEPTes0u4eNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=a83ec650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Booking.com</a> 的廣告，出現以上情況的智能手機包括了 P30 Pro、P20、P20 Pro、P20 Lite、Honor 10、P10 Lite 等型號。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nHuawei<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n有不少 Reddit 的用戶證實，這些廣告似乎是華為手機的&ldquo;雜誌解鎖&rdquo;功能中出現，&ldquo;雜誌解鎖&rdquo;功能允許用戶在其鎖定屏幕上擁有一組旋轉圖像，每次他們解鎖手機時都會出現不同的變化，即使用戶沒有訂閱相關的廣告資訊，亦會有機會在手機上顯示。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n至於 <a href=\"http://Booking.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FBooking.com&d=goC%2B%2BwCxwRgX8SEPTes0u4eNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=a83ec650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Booking.com</a> 的廣告並不是只有發生在單一的國家，並且已在多個國家/地區發現，包括澳大利亞、德國、匈牙利、愛爾蘭、荷蘭、挪威、南非、西班牙、瑞典和英國。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nHuawei<br />\n<br />\nHuawei<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n就此事華為官方已經由德國 Twitter 帳戶作出道歉，表示&ldquo;我們很抱歉這樣的廣告會為用戶帶來不便&rdquo;，並表示這些鎖屏桌布連同廣告已從其伺服器中刪除，但由於某些鎖屏桌布可能已經下載到用戶的設備上，因此必須手動刪除及停用廣告。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n用戶可以通過屏幕上滑動轉到設置&gt;鎖屏&gt;雜誌解鎖來停用廣告圖像，即可以不再使用預設的風景桌布。要進一步作出保護，用家可以從圖庫或文件管理器中刪除與 Magazine unlock 相應的文件夾。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n華為沒有澄清這些是故意上傳還是錯誤上傳，但表明公司目前正在對這起事件進行調查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n圖 原文<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkepc.com/18049\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkepc.com%2F18049&d=goC%2B%2BwCxwRgX8SEPTes0u4eNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=dea50218\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkepc.com/18049</a>"},{"pid":"c4db722d6d78befa0fc2fb4ad706ec4f11a6411a","tid":1235151,"uid":9769,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T06:00:18.000Z","msg":"巴打坐左幾耐？"},{"pid":"be18c1a52a93f4c50df1d9b0451f453fcd03a01a","tid":1235151,"uid":61954,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c4db722d6d78befa0fc2fb4ad706ec4f11a6411a","tid":1235151,"uid":9769,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T06:00:18.000Z","msg":"巴打坐左幾耐？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T06:11:03.000Z","msg":"你又坐咗幾耐？"},{"pid":"0b4675db4461704a4124036840817be012aea53d","tid":1235151,"uid":9769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"be18c1a52a93f4c50df1d9b0451f453fcd03a01a","tid":1235151,"uid":61954,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c4db722d6d78befa0fc2fb4ad706ec4f11a6411a","tid":1235151,"uid":9769,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T06:00:18.000Z","msg":"巴打坐左幾耐？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T06:11:03.000Z","msg":"你又坐咗幾耐？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T06:30:45.000Z","msg":"2年3個月零10日"},{"pid":"1e7461b509f00137e5cbd907c95c44d321c1697a","tid":1235151,"uid":2230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0b4675db4461704a4124036840817be012aea53d","tid":1235151,"uid":9769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"be18c1a52a93f4c50df1d9b0451f453fcd03a01a","tid":1235151,"uid":61954,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c4db722d6d78befa0fc2fb4ad706ec4f11a6411a","tid":1235151,"uid":9769,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T06:00:18.000Z","msg":"巴打坐左幾耐？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T06:11:03.000Z","msg":"你又坐咗幾耐？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T06:30:45.000Z","msg":"2年3個月零10日"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T06:31:32.000Z","msg":"辛苦哂"}]}